query:
-- Get or create San Diego County agency
INSERT IGNORE INTO counties (name, state, usesStateProtocols, protocolVersion, createdAt)
VALUES ('San Diego County EMS', 'California', 0, '2025-2026', NOW());

SET @sd_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%San Diego%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Insert San Diego County treatment protocols from 2025-2026 Protocol Packet
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
-- Patient Management Standards (S-100 series)
(@sd_id, 'S-100', 'Patient Management Standards', 'General', 'San Diego County EMS Patient Management Standards. BLS and ALS transport criteria, patient-centered care modifications, and documentation requirements.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-101', 'Glossary of Terms', 'General', 'San Diego County EMS Glossary of Terms. BE-FAST stroke screening scale, BRUE definition, LEADSD intubation documentation, and other key terminology.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-103', 'Skills List', 'General', 'San Diego County EMS Skills List. Authorized BLS, AEMT, and Paramedic skills and procedures.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'P-115', 'Medication List', 'Medications', 'San Diego County EMS Authorized Medication List. EMT, AEMT, and Paramedic medication formulary with dosages and routes.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),

-- Medical Protocols (S-120 series)
(@sd_id, 'S-121', 'Abdominal Pain', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Abdominal Pain. Assessment, pain management, and transport considerations.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-122', 'Allergic Reaction / Anaphylaxis', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Allergic Reaction and Anaphylaxis. Epinephrine, diphenhydramine, and supportive care.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-123', 'Altered Level of Consciousness (Non-Traumatic)', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Altered Level of Consciousness. Blood glucose assessment, naloxone, and supportive care.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-124', 'Burns', 'Trauma', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Burns. Burn assessment, cooling, fluid resuscitation, and pain management.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),

-- Cardiac Protocols (S-126-S-132)
(@sd_id, 'S-126', 'Discomfort / Pain of Suspected Cardiac Origin', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Chest Pain/ACS. 12-lead ECG, aspirin, nitroglycerin, and STEMI activation criteria.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-127', 'Adjunct Cardiac Devices', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Adjunct Cardiac Devices. LVAD, pacemaker, and ECPR decision algorithm.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-129', 'Cardiac Arrest - Non-Traumatic', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Non-Traumatic Cardiac Arrest. CPR, defibrillation, ACLS medications, and post-resuscitation care.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-130', 'Symptomatic Bradycardia', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Symptomatic Bradycardia. Atropine, transcutaneous pacing, and dopamine.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-131', 'Narrow Complex Tachycardia', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Narrow Complex Tachycardia. Vagal maneuvers, adenosine, and synchronized cardioversion.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-132', 'Wide Complex Tachycardia', 'Cardiac', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Wide Complex Tachycardia. Amiodarone and synchronized cardioversion.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW());
